<h1>Meal Search</h1>
<main>
  <p>Welcome to Meal Search! This site lets you look up meals from TheMealDB by keyword. Enter an ingredient, dish name, or cuisine below and we'll find matching recipes. Click any result to see its full ingredients, instructions, and links.</p>
  <form action="/searchmealsbykeyword" method="POST">
    <label for="keyword">Search by keyword:</label>
    <input type="text" name="keyword" id="keyword">
    <input type="submit" value="Search">
  </form>
</main>
